            <li><strong>Term Life:</strong> Affordable coverage for 10, 20, or 30-year terms</li>
            <li><strong>Whole Life:</strong> Permanent protection with cash value accumulation</li>
            <li><strong>Universal Life:</strong> Flexible premiums and adjustable death benefits</li>
            <li><strong>Final Expense:</strong> Simplified coverage for end-of-life costs</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Policies starting at just <strong>$15/month</strong> with no medical exam options available.</p>
          <a href={url('/contact')} class="btn btn--primary">Get a Life Quote</a>
        </div>
        <div class="two-col__image">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511895426328-dc8714191300?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Happy family together" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Business Insurance -->
  <section class="section section--gray" id="business">
