            <li>General liability insurance</li>
            <li>Commercial property insurance</li>
            <li>Workers' compensation</li>
            <li>Professional liability (E&O)</li>
            <li>Commercial auto insurance</li>
            <li>Cyber liability insurance</li>
            <li>Business interruption coverage</li>
            <li>Directors & officers (D&O) liability</li>
          </ul>
          <p><strong>Industry specialists:</strong> Dedicated teams for construction, healthcare, tech, retail, and hospitality.</p>
          <a href={url('/contact')} class="btn btn--primary">Get a Business Quote</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Health Insurance -->
  <section class="section" id="health">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="two-col">
        <div>
          <h2>üè• Health Insurance</h2>
          <p>Health is wealth. Zava Health Insurance offers comprehensive plans for individuals, families, and employer groups with nationwide provider access.</p>
          <h4>Plan Types</h4>
          <ul style="color: var(--color-gray-600); padding-left: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <li>Individual and family plans (PPO, HMO, EPO)</li>
            <li>Employer-sponsored group plans</li>
            <li>Medicare supplement plans</li>
